com.samsung.android.sdk.health.content

Interface ShealthContract.Constants.MealItemUnit

  • Enclosing interface:
    ShealthContract.Constants

    public static interface ShealthContract.Constants.MealItemUnit
    This interface defines the meal item unit types. The user input is in the standard unit of gram. The rest of the defined units are currently for internal use only.
